iety so not every phrase uses a symmetric parabola: per-phrase random selection from parabolic/cosine/asymmetric-Bezier/flat/inverted with peak-position variance. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-029 | Implement restraint parameter enforced as global dampener across rules. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-030 | Implement R12 Sensor-to-Intent Aggregation Matrix: smoothed IIR + hysteresis → aggregate intentions (global_energy, global_restraint, global_brightness). | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-031 | Implement bounded reactive delta track in scheduler with per-parameter modulation caps. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-032 | Couple narrative engine to SectionEnvelope selection so dramatic arcs drive section choice. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-033 | Expose aggregate-intention telemetry (global_energy/restraint/brightness) in operator diagnostics, never raw one-to-one mappings. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-034 | Build the metric battery: IOI CoV, velocity σ, DNVR/DNODR, pitch-class entropy H1, Grooving Similarity (GS), tempo autocorrelation ρ₁, LZ76 compression ratio, novelty peaks per phrase, silence-at-phrase-boundaries. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-035 | Build anti-pattern tests: quantization ghosting, dynamic compression, motif ossification, random-as-expression (Ljung-Box), symmetric-arc uncanny, dead-silence failure. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-036 | Implement performance-worm logger: 2D trajectory in tempo–loudness space + convex-hull area computation as CI artifact. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-037 | Integrate metric battery + anti-pattern detectors into CI gate with fail-on-regression policy. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-038 | Build audio-rendered SSM + Foote novelty cross-check via librosa on the actual rendered audio. | SHOULD | T2 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-039 | Embed rule-stack provenance in exported audio metadata (e.g., WAV iXML chunk or sidecar JSON) for listener-review workflow. | MUST | T1 |  |\\\\\\\\n+| CCH-040 | Establish listener-revi